                <li>Redesigned the live patching system on GCP, using object storage, Cloud Functions, Load Balancer, CDN, and reduced deployment time from 1 hour to 5 minutes</li>
                <li>Operated multi-cloud deployments using Terraform and Gitlab CI/CD pipelines</li>
                <li>Transformed a monolithic deployment pipeline running on 1 VM to use a GKE cluster, increasing the deployment success rate from 60% to 95%</li>
                <li>Migrated a legacy on-prem monitoring system to Grafana (TIG stack) on a regional GKE cluster</li>
                <li>Deployed automatically more than 2000 game servers on AWS Gamelift using Python scripts</li>
                <li>Managed a micro-services cluster on AWS ECS with CloudFormation</li>
                <li>Developed and shared Python scripts to manage Stadia deployments, now used by a majority of production teams in the studio</li>
                <li>Implemented AWS spot and GCP preemptible VM usage, reducing cloud cost by 50%</li>
