                <li>Migrated a JAVA satellite image processing software to the private cloud. Improved processing time by 20%, and infrastructure deployment time from 5 days to 4 hours</li>
                <li>Trained a 20 people team to use OpenStack, and delivered cloud best practices</li>
                <li>Migrated a JAVA mission planning app to Docker, reduced the installation time from 4 hours to 15 minutes</li>
                <li>Designed a public cloud architecture for the ESA (Sobloo) using OpenStack to handle 5 PB of image data</li>
                <li>Deployed and managed a 100 nodes Kubernetes cluster on the public cloud using kubeadm</li>
